org.apache.hive.hcatalog.templeton

Class JsonBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hive.hcatalog.templeton.JsonBuilder

  • public class JsonBuilder
extends Object
    Helper class to build new json objects with new top level properties. Only add non-null entries.
